# ─── Pitch test plan — INTERNAL (item 62) ─────────────────────────────────────
# Full ablation + multi-tenant validation + GCP-ops harness, built for internal
# benefit (multi-tenant = PAID-adjacent), not a customer artifact. OSS ships a
# lean examples/benchmark/ reproducible proof instead. Excluded wholesale.
pitch-test-plan/
# The pitch-comparison Grafana dashboard is the visualisation front-end for the
# internal harness above: every panel filters on the synthetic user_ids
# (pitch-optimized@pitch.test / pitch-baseline@pitch.test) + complexity_tier that
# ONLY run_roi_pitch.py emits, so it shows "No data" for any OSS self-hoster.
dashboard/dashboards/pitch-comparison.json

